name: markupsafe
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "MarkupSafe" %}
{% set version = "1.0" %}
{% set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{% set hash = "a6be69091dac236ea9c6bc7d012beab42010fa914c459791d627dad4910eb665" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - markupsafe

about:
  home: https://www.palletsprojects.com/p/markupsafe/
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A Python module that implements the jinja2.Markup string
  dev_url: https://github.com/pallets/markupsafe

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pelson
    - scopatz
